{"tid":1450694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「黑警還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:59:09.000Z","uid":197005,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4fd197cce200827016bc66cf704d25de74ee30cb","tid":1450694,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:50:15.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，先去連登肯出post先，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「黑警還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\nTG群組，不停轉發出去，勢要討回雙眼，嬲到火屎呀<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2Smgqvg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=542f6b5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2Smgqvg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=8f148612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a><br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是我們的責任，因為機場不夠大，圍到出青馬，因為條橋唔夠闊。<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，要入健力士，留傳歷史<br />\n「黑警還眼 / an eye for an eye」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你入機場殺死所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停"},{"pid":"5dcb1522877604e1a942a422f76b20bb04282f70","tid":1450694,"uid":228175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:54:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ba6343d6d330577bac6735418cfbd1e82a948da","tid":1450694,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dcb1522877604e1a942a422f76b20bb04282f70","tid":1450694,"uid":228175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:54:04.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:54:41.000Z","msg":"要洗 麻煩絲打開post<i